Class Quartet<A extends com.google.protobuf.Message,B,C,D>

  • java.lang.Object

    All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Iterable<com.google.protobuf.Message>

    public final class Quartet<A extends com.google.protobuf.Message,B,C,D>
extends Tuple
    A tuple with four elements.

    The first element must be a non-default Message (and not Empty).

    Other three can be Message, Optional or Either.
